details.name: Call Down
details.description: Call down an aerial missile strike on enemy units in a target area.  Two missiles arrive in succession, the first dealing major damage and minor slow for 2 seconds; the second dealing minor damage and major slow for 4 seconds. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Adds a Side Gunner that at random attacks enemy units within a 600 radius every 1.1 seconds.
